  "subject": "Update java base image",
  "commit_message": "Update java base image\n\n- use eclipse-temurin:11-jre-alpine\n- change the backend url that is used in the frontend [0]\n\n[0] the backend and frontend are served in one tomcat container.\nIn the past, the backend url that was configured in the frontend\nwas set to a nodeport address. Nodeports are not used anymore.\nInstead window.location.origin is used which will use the ingress\nurl of the frontend.\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4163\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <Fiete.Ostkamp@telekom.de>\nChange-Id: Ie7aa6151e88493d7a62acefc82472699684e3e99\n",
